{"id":231,"date":"2021-09-14T13:43:00","date_gmt":"2021-09-14T04:43:00","guid":{"rendered":"https://haru-network.net/?p=231"},"modified":"2021-09-14T13:43:00","modified_gmt":"2021-09-14T04:43:00","slug":"chromebook-shortcutapplication","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/231/","title":{"rendered":"[Chromebook] アプリのショートカット"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">注意事項</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Chromebookでは、デスクトップ(「壁紙」の部分)にファイルやアイコンを配置することはできません。</p>\n\n\n\n<!--more-->\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">ショートカットの作り方</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>「デスクトップ」ではなく、その下にある<strong>「シェルフ」と呼ばれる部分にアプリやショートカットを配置する事ができま</strong>す。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img data-attachment-id=\"236\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/231/attachment/screenshot-2021-09-14-13-47-08/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-13.47.08.png\" data-orig-size=\"1366,768\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot-2021-09-14-13.47.08\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-13.47.08-300x169.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-13.47.08-1024x576.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-13.47.08-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-236\" width=\"527\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-13.47.08-1024x576.png 1024w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-13.47.08-300x169.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-13.47.08-768x432.png 768w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-13.47.08.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 527px) 100vw, 527px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\">※ファイルのショートカットは置けません。</span></p>\n\n\n\n<p>シェルフに新しく「アプリ」を配置する簡単な方法は、</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>シェルフに表示された固定したいアプリのアイコンを 右クリック or 長押し(タッチパネルの場合) して「固定」をクリック</strong>することで、シェルフに固定することができます。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" data-attachment-id=\"243\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/231/attachment/screenshot-2021-09-14-15-02-40/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-15.02.40.png\" data-orig-size=\"1366,768\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot-2021-09-14-15.02.40\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-15.02.40-300x169.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-15.02.40-1024x576.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-14-15.02.40-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-243\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/